When summoned, a naked version of lydia appears to fight for you for 60 seconds. She doens´t have a weapon and only attacks when u attack. She can´t be talked to.
I only made this spell for fun. You can kill her an unlimited amount of times.

If you want some changes on her, let me know and i´ll see what I can do.
Also, if someone wants me to, I can make one where she is geared up and ready to go.
